# Linux Packages to install via system package manager
# One package per line - works with apt (Ubuntu/Debian) and dnf (Fedora)
#
# === Editors ===
# neovim              # Modern Vim fork with better defaults
# vim-gtk3            # Vim with clipboard support
# emacs               # GNU Emacs editor
# code                # VS Code (requires Microsoft repository)
# sublime-text        # Sublime Text (requires repository)
#
